An 8 AM to 3 PM shift, Monday through Friday, with a 30-minute lunch each day, breaks down like this:

  • Daily hours worked:
    7 hours total 0.5 hour lunch = 6.5 hours/day

  • Weekly total (Monday to Friday):

So you're working 32.5 hours per week under that schedule.
